-- Pirelli Swings to First-Half Net Loss on Impact of Real Estate Separation
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-29T12:34:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/pirelli-swings-to-first-half-net-loss-on-impact-of-real-estate-separation.html

          
          
             Pirelli SpA posted a net loss of
165.5 million euros in the first half versus a profit a year
earlier, because of effects of the separation of its real estate
unit, the Italian company said in a statement distributed by the
Italian exchange  
          
          


  


        